{"tid":1728742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實可以用ai破壞林奠同cctvb喺藍絲之中嘅公信力","createTime":"2019-11-17T04:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:12:52.000Z","uid":132859,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b9bb2c86bd70499a51ba393a193c42a1ece1d04","tid":1728742,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:00:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標</span></span><br />\n藍絲睇新聞嗰陣覺得林鄭同埋cctvb代表公權力 <br />\n講乜都信<br />\n要破壞政府公信力<br />\n就要將呢兩個symbols嘅公信力破壞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">方法</span></span><br />\n用ai 去複製林鄭月娥同cctvb主播把聲<br />\n再用deepfake改佢哋口型<br />\n配合剪片之下<br />\n將呢啲片喺whatsapp傳出去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">內容</span></span><br />\n一部分係半真半假<br />\n一部分係大部分真小部分假<br />\n最後一部份就係全部假到冇得再假嘅內容<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">endgame</span></span><br />\n玩到藍絲唔再識分真假tvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜都唔再信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35821869d38057edb3731e8e707fc4e36e9533af","tid":1728742,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>他們在打的是「中共政權保衛戰」，而你們僅僅是在打「香港生活方式保衛戰」</strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，<strong>第一就是分化</strong>，<strong>把勇武派、和理非派拆分</strong>，<strong>第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」</strong>，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後<strong>隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒</strong>。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，<strong>但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能</strong>，坦白說，<strong>還是太嫩</strong>。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是<strong>北京</strong>要製造的<strong>焦點轉移</strong>。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong>。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"52a67a03c0cae394663575464be54a4522062fce","tid":1728742,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:04:41.000Z","msg":"佢哋會唔會都照信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0116aac2404ac49368a38f6f9b6aac8070ef445","tid":1728742,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"係咪剩係得我一個on99,每朝等開花<br />\n<br />\n［中場檢討］ 係黎明行動，唔係黃昏行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}